{"tid":354823,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇經車行買車中伏經驗分享","createTime":"2017-08-10T18:54:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T08:41:00.000Z","uid":3912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a494c0d187e20ff61f91f6367b989c8c6f1da455","tid":354823,"uid":3912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T18:54:06.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 早排買完㗎vw，睇落新新淨淨冇乜問題咪數又少 快快趣趣就扑左鎚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 早兩日同幾個fd出嚟車聚咁啱有個fd攞咗電腦出嚟 就順手叫佢篤下我部車，結果篤一篤發現原來有好幾個地方都著咗燈 但俾人刻意刪咗有問題嘅資料，只係著咗燈但有關問題資料一片空白，車頭顯示連code都冇著<br />\n<br />\n不過好彩都唔係啲好大問題，整返都唔貴，聽日再攞去車房篤大電腦睇下有冇改過個咪數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee4517fd0c0550cb40586b540dbd633e146a337","tid":354823,"uid":13556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T22:18:29.000Z","msg":"車行賣車一定消晒code"},{"pid":"50f984c33605714c3d2f5347818616f87f3f9f4f","tid":354823,"uid":3912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:54:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>車行賣車一定消晒code</blockquote><br />\n我第一次經車行買真係唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩而家篤咗電腦冇乜大問題 咪數亦冇改動"},{"pid":"f01f045a6ff7d55ee66ca33b165cb94c0aaefad5","tid":354823,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:56:02.000Z","msg":"無驗車？"},{"pid":"b131de33db05871027bbcfad467041af181f88b7","tid":354823,"uid":39781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T14:57:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>車行賣車一定消晒code</blockquote><br />\n我第一次經車行買真係唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩而家篤咗電腦冇乜大問題 咪數亦冇改動</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n街外電腦check唔到有冇郁到咪數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定要原廠電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c117ef37ba